      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COMPTON STELLA (4) is yet to miss the placings in an excellent record this track and trip which boasts four wins and six placings. In the money last time at this track (23.52) in a Grade 6, finishing a 3 length third. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. LADY BOMBSHELL (2) rocketed out of the inside draw with a strong early sectional and gave a sight but had to settle for a placing, finishing second (23.42) at this track over 400m. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Leading chance. JAJA DING DONG (6) broke a string of placings finishing in the money two on end before a last start fifth (18.42) at this track. Solid formlines coming through her last run. Leading chance. TESTED (8) placed last start at this track and distance and is in the mix again.",
